text: Been with Dr. Shauna for over a year now, and she has been amazing every single time! She always ensures I'm comfortable during procedures and provides such a sense of reassurance. On top of that, her skincare recommendations are spot on and have worked wonders for me. She truly knows what she's doing! Highly recommended!

Great and pleasant experience under the skilful hands of Dr Shauna Tan. Dr Shauna is not only attentive to details but her suggested treatment protocol using fillers worked wonders on my face. The hollows on my face look plump and naturally lifted. My fine lines were also erased as a result. What i see and have now is a subtle yet youthful v-shaped face and appearance. Really happy with the results, and yes! A big thank you and shoutout to Dr Shauna Tan for her expert advice and treatment plan.

Dr Shauna is outgoing and friendly, and wants the best outcome for her clients.

I've been receiving laser treatment for sun spots/pigmentation from Dr Shauna for around a year, and am pleased to see steady improvement. She also administered Profhilo injections for me on three occasions - the procedure was fast with minimal pain thanks to her quick hands.

Will definitely recommend if you're looking for a knowledgeable and skilled doctor to address your skincare concerns!

Dr Shauna is knowledgeable and meticulous with her work. She always goes above and beyond to provide the best services for her clients. She gives great advice about the work that should be done. As a first time patient for aesthetics, I felt safe and cared for and will recommend her to all my friends and family members.

Dr Shauna has always been so patient and reassuring during treatments! Also super generous sharing her knowledge on skincare, I have learnt so much more on how to take good care of my skin after knowing her.
